name: Sugar Cane Farming Packet
description: The Sugar Cane Farming Packet is unlocked in theWorkshopon theSpace Stationand is equipped in the Prospectors loadout before starting a new prospect. Only after landing on Icarus can the packet be consumed, giving the Prospector fiveSugar CaneSeeds, which then can be planted inDirt MoundsorCrop Plotsto growPlant Resources.
